But the Batman has a few tricks up his sleeve.

Plot Summary

This issue of My Greatest Adventure contains the following three stories:

  • I Was Big Game on Neptune!
  • I Battled the Duplicate Men!
  • I Was the Last Martian!

It also features the following comic strip:

  • Moolah the Mystic

I Was Big Game on Neptune

George Weller was a big game hunter who was abducted by a group of aliens from Neptune! Now a captive on a foreign planet he must work with his fellow captives, various members of other planets, in an attempt to survive being hunted down and potentially escape the planet!

I Battled the Duplicate Men

Adventures Incorporated is responsible for providing thrills and excitement for those willing to pay the price; however, things get all too real when a new category of adventure is added to the program, The Plateau of Duplicate Men!

I Was the Last Martian

After being banished from his own planet, K'ra the Martian heads to Earth in an attempt to protect them from the horrors and dangers that await in outer space. K'ra begins to regret his decision when everyone on Earth is hostile towards him. Will K'ra continue to try and act as Earth's savior or will his experiences cause him to become it's destroyer?

Moolah the Mystic

Moolah and his friend deal with car trouble using Moolah's magic carpet!
name: I Was the Last Martian!

description:
Around the World in 80 Minutes

Paris! The Sahara Desert! Tibet--and the Pacific Ocean! The Flash, Fastest Man Alive, rockets to those distant places and in the most astonishing adventure of all times--answers startling appeals for help and still whirls "Around the World in 80 Minutes!"

Master of the Elements

It was the most astonishing duel ever fought on earth! On one side was the scientific criminal armed with the elements of nature as his weapon--while on the other side was the Flash, who found to his dismay that even his vaunted super-speed was a match for the Criminal-Elemental arsenal of "The Master of the Elements!"
name: Around the World in 80 Minutes! / Master of The Elements
